Introduction:

This archive encompasses all of the monsters as found in the Net Monster
Manual (the version I have, anyway).

This was originally intended for use with the ImpPro software package
(available at Aminet, too, same directory as this, beta version). Big
thanks to Zach Forsyth for his great program, if you are a DM and a
programmer, make some modules for it.



How to use this:

- Unpack the archive.
- Make an assign to ImpPro:
- Make this directory; Data/ExtMonsterData/ under ImpPro:
- Copy the monsters to this directory.
- Now you are guaranteed that the X-refs function.



How to use this with ImpPro:

- Unpack the archive into ImpPro:Data/ExtMonsterData/
- Edit the monster database (or wait for my version).



